♪ You ♪

01:37:48.947 --> 01:37:51.697
♪ Independence comes
with a price ♪

01:37:51.783 --> 01:37:55.663
♪ And questioning
your own advice ♪

01:37:55.745 --> 01:37:58.455
♪ But I know
I’ll be all right ♪

01:37:58.540 --> 01:38:00.210
♪ With an open door ♪

01:38:00.292 --> 01:38:04.552
♪ No matter what I do ♪

01:38:04.629 --> 01:38:07.719
♪ What I do ♪

01:38:07.799 --> 01:38:14.009
♪ Mm, but I see the world
so different now ♪

01:38:15.265 --> 01:38:18.095
♪ That there’s a place
by the sea ♪

01:38:18.184 --> 01:38:22.064
♪ And that’s my town ♪

01:38:22.147 --> 01:38:25.567
♪ When I don’t know
what to say ♪

01:38:25.650 --> 01:38:28.990
♪ When I don’t
know what to do ♪

01:38:29.070 --> 01:38:32.530
♪ There’s a room
I need to sit in ♪

01:38:32.616 --> 01:38:35.826
♪ Surrounded by
my favorite view ♪

01:38:35.910 --> 01:38:39.460
♪ When I need a hand to hold ♪

01:38:39.539 --> 01:38:42.919
♪ Someone to tell the truth ♪

01:38:43.001 --> 01:38:48.591
♪ Would it be okay
if I came home to you? ♪

01:38:50.884 --> 01:38:54.974
♪ No, I don’t want
to keep on going ♪

01:38:55.055 --> 01:38:58.135
♪ When I’m miles away ♪

01:38:58.224 --> 01:39:02.234
♪ And you’re too far away ♪

01:39:02.312 --> 01:39:04.442
♪ Oh ♪

01:39:04.522 --> 01:39:08.492
♪ But if I need you
to remind me ♪

01:39:08.568 --> 01:39:10.358
♪ That nothing has changed ♪

01:39:10.445 --> 01:39:13.865
♪ Would it be okay,
would it be okay ♪

01:39:13.948 --> 01:39:17.038
♪ For you? ♪

01:39:17.118 --> 01:39:22.828
♪ And I see the world
so different now ♪

01:39:24.084 --> 01:39:26.714
♪ ’Cause there’s a place
by the sea ♪

01:39:26.795 --> 01:39:30.795
♪ And that’s my town ♪

01:39:30.882 --> 01:39:34.302
♪ When I don’t know
what to say ♪

01:39:34.386 --> 01:39:37.596
♪ When I don’t
know what to do ♪

01:39:37.681 --> 01:39:41.141
♪ There’s a room
I need to sit in ♪

01:39:41.226 --> 01:39:44.436
♪ Surrounded by
my favorite view ♪

01:39:44.521 --> 01:39:47.981
♪ When I need a hand to hold ♪

01:39:48.066 --> 01:39:51.436
♪ Someone to tell the truth ♪

01:39:51.528 --> 01:39:57.698
♪ Would it be okay
if I came home to you? ♪

01:39:57.784 --> 01:40:00.254
♪ No, would it be okay ♪

01:40:00.328 --> 01:40:04.708
♪ If I came home to you? ♪

01:40:04.791 --> 01:40:06.711
(song ends)

01:40:06.793 --> 01:40:08.843
(wind whistling)
